Package regexio

Class Regex

java.lang.Object
regexio.Regex
public class Regex
extends java.lang.Object
This class can be used to create regex patterns in string form. The patterns can be built using a builder pattern, which makes the regex more readable and more accessible. After all regex operations have been defined, the regex can be built out into a string.
Author:
jonas.franz

    • operations

      private java.util.List<Regex.RegexOperation> operations
      All operations in this regex. When the regex is built, all operations are concatenated after one another to form the final regex.
